Elementeer App Support
Welcome to the official support hub for Elementeer App! We're here to help you with any questions, issues, or feedback you might have.

How to Get Support
Before opening a new issue, please take a moment to:

Check Existing Issues/Discussions: Someone else might have already reported the same issue or asked a similar question. Searching through existing entries can often provide a quick solution.
For Bug Reports:
If you've found a bug or something isn't working as expected, please open a new "Issue" and provide the following details:

What you did: Describe the steps you took that led to the bug.
What you expected to happen: Describe the correct behavior.
What actually happened: Describe the incorrect behavior you observed.
Screenshots/Videos (if applicable): Visuals are incredibly helpful!
Your operating system and browser (if applicable): e.g., Windows 10, Chrome latest; iOS 17, Safari.
Elementeer App version (if applicable):
For Feature Requests:
Have an idea for a new feature or an improvement? We'd love to hear it! Please open a new "Issue" and describe:

The feature you'd like: Explain your idea clearly.
Why it would be useful: Describe the problem it solves or the benefit it provides.
Any alternatives you've considered:
For General Questions & Discussions:
For general questions, "how-to" inquiries, or to engage in broader discussions about Elementeer App, please use the Discussions tab (if enabled).

Our Goal
We aim to make Elementeer App the best it can be, and your feedback is crucial to that goal. We appreciate your patience as we work to address all inquiries.

Thank you for using Elementeer App!
